# Seite 6 – Best Practices

Zum Beispiel:

| Do                  | Don't                  |
| ------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Small commits       | Huge commits           |
| Meaningful comments | "Update"               |
| One topic per PR    | Many unrelated changes |
| Test before commit  | Commit untested SQL    |

